# Drop your custom Odoo addons in this directory.
#
# Each addon lives in its own subdirectory at the top level here:
#
#   odoo/addons/
#   ├── my_module_a/
#   │   ├── __init__.py
#   │   ├── __manifest__.py
#   │   └── ...
#   └── my_module_b/
#       └── ...
#
# This directory is mounted into the Odoo container at
# /mnt/extra-addons (see docker-compose.yml) and registered in the
# addons_path of odoo.conf.
#
# After adding a module, install it from the Odoo UI (Apps menu) or
# from the CLI inside the container:
#
#   docker compose exec odoo odoo -d <db_name> -i <module_name> --stop-after-init
